title: Bed Time Stories for Aidan Christopher 001
creator: Various
description: Librivox recording of bed time stories. Bed time Stories for Aidan Christopher is a collection of: Favorite stories submitted and read by the Volunteers at Librivox.org. This project has been undertaken to celebrate the October 2007 arrival into the world of: Aidan Christopher ! (Description written by: Robert Scott) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audiobooks or to become a volunteer reader, please visit librivox.org M4B format available
subject: librivox; audiobook; nursery rhymes
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
